-Yes.

453
00:29:33.542 --> 00:29:35.250
So. you just dropped her off over there?

454
00:29:35.667 --> 00:29:38.167
No. his daughters
invited her over to play.

455
00:29:40.500 --> 00:29:42.625
You need to stop being so hard on George.

456
00:29:42.708 --> 00:29:46.167
He likes you.
and he's being really helpful.

457
00:29:46.250 --> 00:29:47.375
