467
00:30:19.792 --> 00:30:20.625
Ramen.

468
00:30:21.583 --> 00:30:23.625
Really? That's funny.

469
00:30:24.625 --> 00:30:25.458
Is it?

470
00:30:26.333 --> 00:30:27.667
