472
00:30:32.792 --> 00:30:35.125
This is the third place
you've taken him to.

473
00:30:35.208 --> 00:30:37.167
Yeah. he's actually
still at the repair shop.

474
00:30:37.250 --> 00:30:40.292
I'm… having a part examined.

475
00:30:40.917 --> 00:30:41.958
By a specialist.

476
00:30:42.333 --> 00:30:44.667
So. is he gonna be
up and running again soon?

477
00:30:45.667 --> 00:30:47.083
I'm not sure.

478
00:30:47.167 --> 00:30:49.833
You know. it's… It's complicated.

479
00:30:53.042 --> 00:30:54.625
That's Mika. I got to go.

480
00:31:01.458 --> 00:31:03.417
Functions like any other reader.

481
00:31:03.500 --> 00:31:04.792
Should be intuitive.

482
00:31:04.875 --> 00:31:05.917
Do I need a code?

483
00:31:06.792 --> 00:31:09.625
Yeah. there should be a certification card
that came with Yang.

484
00:31:09.708 --> 00:31:12.250
There's a serial number and a PIN on it.

485
00:31:12.333 --> 00:31:13.958
Also. per our agreement.

486
00:31:14.042 --> 00:31:16.125
you'll need to bring
Yang's body here tomorrow.

487
00:31:16.208 --> 00:31:17.292
-Sooner the better.
-Yes.

488
00:31:17.375 --> 00:31:22.125
I wouldn't be surprised if Russ is trying
to replace parts and steal the originals.

489
00:31:22.958 --> 00:31:27.583
We will keep Yang's body
preserved here in a bio-state

490
00:31:27.667 --> 00:31:30.542
while you go and review the memories

491
00:31:31.333 --> 00:31:33.292
and decide what you want to do next.

492
00:31:33.375 --> 00:31:35.833
Okay. Yeah. Thank you.

493
00:31:35.917 --> 00:31:37.167
Thank you.

494
00:31:37.250 --> 00:31:40.500
I've dedicated my life
to understanding techno-sapiens. This…

495
00:31:41.417 --> 00:31:42.375
This is a gift.

496
00:32:10.792 --> 00:32:15.625
I wanna be just like the wind

497
00:32:15.708 --> 00:32:19.250
Just flowing in the air

498
00:32:19.333 --> 00:32:23.167
Flowing in open space

499
