Yang taught you that?

500
00:32:26.625 --> 00:32:29.708
It's his favorite song. Do you like it?

501
00:32:31.083 --> 00:32:32.292
I love it.

502
00:32:39.958 --> 00:32:40.875
Hey.

503
00:32:42.292 --> 00:32:43.625
Mika's up late.

504
00:32:45.917 --> 00:32:47.083
She couldn't sleep.

505
00:32:49.625 --> 00:32:50.792
You going somewhere?

506
00:32:52.375 --> 00:32:54.250
Brenda's meeting me at the office.

507
00:32:54.333 --> 00:32:56.333
We're gonna stay overnight and work.

508
00:32:57.208 --> 00:32:58.083
We're behind.

509
00:32:59.625 --> 00:33:01.583
I'm sorry I wasn't here earlier.

510
00:33:01.667 --> 00:33:02.583
It's fine.

511
00:33:04.875 --> 00:33:07.875
You'll need to take Mika to school
and get her ready for the day.

512
00:33:08.250 --> 00:33:09.750
Do you think you can do that?

513
00:33:09.833 --> 00:33:10.792
Yeah. of course.

514
00:33:13.125 --> 00:33:15.667
All right. I need to go.

515
00:33:15.750 --> 00:33:17.000
Are we okay?

516
00:33:21.583 --> 00:33:23.208
So. what did the part reveal?

517
00:33:24.667 --> 00:33:25.500
The part?

518
00:33:27.958 --> 00:33:28.792
The part.

