00:33:33.375 --> 00:33:34.333
Yeah. yeah.

521
00:33:38.125 --> 00:33:40.542
We should know something soon.

522
00:33:44.917 --> 00:33:45.917
I need to go.

523
00:33:48.333 --> 00:33:50.083
Try and get some sleep if you can.

524
00:34:03.500 --> 00:34:10.500
Serial 733951137CM99.

